these are the files we use (path in original site -> path in this project (root/locales/...)

cgi/cgi-{lang}.xml                               -> data/cgi-{lang}.xml
cgi/index-{lang}.xml                             -> data/index-{lang}.xml
dtd/can{lang}.dtd                                -> data/can{lang}.dtd
(definition file, unused?) corpus.dtd            -> data/corpus.dtd
(definition file, unused?) cgi-translations.dtd  -> data/cgi-translations.dtd


after making modifications to data files, run

   ./make_final.py {lang}.json

to regenerate the {lang}.json file

